'''Christiane Chabi-Kao''' (wavutse ku ya 30 Kamena 1963) ni umuyobozi wa filime wo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] akaba n'umwanditsi.<ref>Christiane Chabi Kao - Fiche Personne sur Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › personnes</ref>

== Ubuzima ==
Chabi-Kao yavukiye i Marseille mu [[Bufaransa]] mu 1963.  Yize muri Kaminuza ya Reims Champagne-Ardenne kuva 1984 kugeza 1986<ref>Christiane CHABI KAO (COTONOU, REIMS) - Copains d'avant <nowiki>https://copainsdavant.linternaute.com</nowiki> › ...</ref>. Mu 1990, Chabi-Kao yasubiye muri [[Afurika]].  Yasohokanye na filime ye ya mbere, ''Les enfants esclaves'', mu 2005, documentaire isobanura abana b'abacakara bigezweho<ref>Christiane Chabi Kao - AFRICINE .org <nowiki>https://www.africine.org</nowiki> › personne</ref>. 

Mu 2007, yayoboye filime ''Les inseparables''. Ivuga amateka y'abavandimwe Yawa na Abi, se bamugurisha ku mucuruza w'abana, maze nyina ajya mu ishami rishinzwe kurengera abana rya Polisi kugira ngo amenye uko byagenze.<ref>Benin filmmaker takes fight against child labour to school <nowiki>https://www.expatica.com</nowiki> › Home › News</ref> Iyi filime yakozwe na UNICEF na Radiyo na Televiziyo y'igihugu ya [[Bénin]] (ORTB), isohoka nk'uruhererekane rwa firime enye<ref>Christiane Chabi Kao: Festival Lagunimages - 05 to 08 ... <nowiki>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com</nowiki> › 2013/12</ref>. Chabi-Kao yanditse iyi filime mu rwego rwo gukangurira no guhagarika icuruzwa ry'abana.<ref>Christiane Chabi-Kao - AlloCiné (allocine.fr)</ref>  Yakiriye igihembo nyafurika Numerique mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique ryabereye i Montreal mu 2008, anahabwa igihembo cy’uburenganzira bwa muntu mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi na Televiziyo rya Panafrican 2009 rya Ouagadougou. <ref>A cinema lesson by Christiane Chabi Kao | Europeana <nowiki>https://www.europeana.eu</nowiki> › item</ref> Nyuma yo kumenyeshwa itegeko ribuza kwerekanwa ku buntu, Chabi-Kao yateguye kwerekana filime ku banyeshuri 300 ba Burkinabe<ref>Christiane Chabi Kao Photos and Premium High Res Pictures ... <nowiki>https://www.gettyimages.com</nowiki> › photos › christiane-chabi-...</ref>. 

Mu 2009, yasimbuye Monique Mbeke Phoba nk'umuyobozi w'ikirori cya Lagunimages i Cotonou .  Nkumuyobozi, Chabi-Kao afasha kwambara iserukiramuco rya firime ryizina rimwe.<ref>Christiane Chabi-Kao - Filmographie - Télérama.fr <nowiki>https://www.telerama.fr</nowiki> › personnalite</ref>  Yakoreye iserukiramuco imyaka itari mike mbere yo kuba umuyobozi, ahabwa inkunga na Deutsche Welle Academy yo kwiga uko bategura ibirori<ref>Christiane Chabi-Kao - SensaCine.com <nowiki>https://www.sensacine.com</nowiki> › actors</ref>. Chabi-Kao yanditse akanayobora ibiganiro bya televiziyo ''bigizwe n'ibice 14'' muri Les Chenapans muri 2013. Irerekana ubuzima nintambara byingimbi batanu bo muri Bénin, kandi ikoresha abakinnyi badafite umwuga<ref>Chenapans (Les) - Images francophones <nowiki>https://www.imagesfrancophones.org</nowiki> › ...</ref>. 

